################################################################################
# Notes:
################################################################################
# 1. MAC addresses must match those in ggNet backend database
# 2. Fixed IPs should be outside DHCP range or use reservations
# 3. Group names are for organization only, not enforced by DHCP
# 4. Per-machine iPXE scripts generated by: pxe/service.py
# 5. To reload config: systemctl restart isc-dhcp-server
# 6. Test with: dhcpd -t -cf /etc/dhcp/dhcpd.conf
